# List the JIRA items included in this pull request  #
[WPO-13767 - Incomplete specific activity view models](https://wealthdynamixltd.atlassian.net/browse/WPO-13767)

# Description #
The view models for specific activity sub-types do not contain all the fields from the sub-types. For example, “PrimaryCode” is missing from `VmPhoneCall`, `VmCallback` and others.

Usually bespoke fields are returned in the `AdditionalAttributes`. But the logic populates the AdditionalAttributes by including in there only fields that are not in the model class, CrmPhoneCall etc. In this case those fields are in the model class and are therefore missing from both the main section and AdditionalAttributes of the response.
